    <h1>How to Choose an <em>Operator.</em></h1>
    <p>There are over 200 Kilimanjaro operators based in Tanzania. The differences between them are not always visible until you're on the mountain. Here are the questions to ask before you book, the red flags to spot, and what the safety standard actually looks like.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book With Us &#x2192;</a>
